item.title: CVE-2022-3086|2024-08-03T01:00:10.222Z -- cradlepoint -- ibr600
item.description: Cradlepoint IBR600 NCOS versions 6.5.0.160bc2e and prior are vulnerable to shell escape, which enables local attackers with non-superuser credentials to gain full, unrestrictive shell access which may allow an attacker to execute arbitrary code.
